[23/01/2018 03:53:58] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[23/01/2018 03:54:01] <font color="#ffff00">Firth Clark,</font>
[23/01/2018 03:54:01] <font color="#ffff00">mi inspector de calidad</font>
