[23/01/2018 23:06:34] <font color="#ffff00">(R E)</font>
[23/01/2018 23:06:46] <font color="#ffff00">(GIME)</font>
[23/01/2018 23:06:51] <font color="#0000ff">(Obras)</font>
[23/01/2018 23:06:54] <font color="#ffff00">(SUSPIRA) Ha sido</font>
[23/01/2018 23:06:54] <font color="#ffff00">una idea desafortunada.</font>
[23/01/2018 23:06:56] <font color="#00ff00">Yo ya lo suponía.</font>
[23/01/2018 23:07:00] <font color="#00ff00">Pero no quería</font>
[23/01/2018 23:07:00] <font color="#00ff00">desilusionarte otra vez.</font>
[23/01/2018 23:07:02] <font color="#ffff00">¿Cuánto tiempo has dicho</font>
[23/01/2018 23:07:02] <font color="#ffff00">que faltaba?</font>
